title: GitLab security advisory (AV25-166)
description: On March 26, 2025, GitLab published a security advisory to address vulnerabilities in the following products:
products: GitLab Community Edition (CE)  versions prior to 17.10.1, 17.9.3 and 17.8.6
GitLab Enterprise Edition (EE)  versions prior to 17.10.1, 17.9.3 and 17.8.6
solution: Review the references and apply the necessary updates.
